Package edu.cmu.hw2.annotators

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GoldPipelineAnnotator
    Initialize with the Gold Pipeline method.
    NameEntityAnnotator
    This classes reads the annotated name entities and used these name entites to score an existing question.
    NGramAnnotator
    This processor tries its best to implement the N-Gram method.
    NGramScoring
    This class generally does the NGram scoring based on the NGrams the docs generate.
    ScorePrintAnnotator
    After all the answers have been processed by the scoring method, this class simply reads the answers and prints them out.
    ScorePrinter
    This class mainly generates the score and prints out the scores.
    TextElementAnnotator
    This class is the initial step to annotate the document with Question and Answer type.
    TokenAnnotator
    This step is the second step in annotation.
    TokenOverlapAnnotator
    This annotator uses the tokens generated before to score the answers.
Author:
jerry This package uses the existing type systems to generate the Annotation used to parse and analyze the input data.
